item.title: Mock Tech Interviews
item.description: Tech Mock Interview Practice job interview with ISC2 NBC security professional interviewers from top companies and receive feedback on your performance. How Does it Work? Submit a request here Schedule the interview - The board members will review the request, schedule an interviewer based on the provided available time slots, and send you a Zoom calendar invite. Complete the mock Interview - The interview will be recorded just for you and the interviewer.
